data.description: Welcome to this stunning 5-bedroom, 4.5-bathroom home in Stone Mountain, GA, offering a perfect blend of elegance and modern functionality. Located just 2 miles from Hwy 78, 6 miles from I-285, and 3 miles from the iconic Stone Mountain Park, this residence is conveniently situated near various amenities located in much sought after Parkview High School District.    As you enter, you'll find the primary ensuite on the main floor, providing convenience and accessibility. The main floor also hosts a well-equipped laundry room, ensuring efficiency in your daily routines. The kitchen offers access to a screened-in porch, perfect for enjoying the outdoors while maintaining comfort.    The second floor boasts three bedrooms and two full bathrooms, accompanied by two family rooms that provide versatile living spaces. The upper floor features an additional bedroom, a full bathroom, and yet another family room, offering flexibility for various needs.    For car enthusiasts or those needing ample storage, the property includes a 3-car garage with four overhead hanging storage racks and a convenient deep sink. The garage also houses a 27-panel 9kWh solar panel system, complemented by a 13kWh Tesla backup battery, contributing to energy efficiency and sustainability.    This smart home is equipped with several intelligent features, enhancing convenience and control. Enjoy the fenced-in backyard, providing privacy and a secure space for outdoor activities. The property includes a water filtration system, ensuring access to clean and purified water.    Flexibility is key in this home, with abundant flex spaces that can be customized for various purposes, meeting the unique needs of the homeowner. Outside the garage, there's ample parking space for up to 9 cars, ideal for hosting gatherings or accommodating a larger household.    With a location just 1 mile from the library, parks, and an elementary school, this home combines the tranquility of its surroundings with the convenience of nearby amenities. Don't miss the opportunity to make this meticulously designed and well-appointed residence your own.    Schedule a tour TODAY!
